    <div style="font-size:12px;line-height:16px;color:#15243B;">Title of hero-step</div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;line-height:15px;margin-top:2px;">
      <span style="color:#15243B;font-weight:600;">Due 13 Jul 2026 (estimated)</span>
      <span style="color:#4A5A70;"> · Required · official requirement</span>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;color:#5B6B80;margin-top:2px;word-break:break-all;">Official source: https://example.gob.es/tramite</div>
  </div><div style="page-break-inside:avoid;padding:8px 0 8px 12px;border-left:3px solid #2B5AA3;border-bottom:1px solid #D8D2C8;">
    <div style="font-size:12px;line-height:16px;color:#15243B;">Title of overdue-step</div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;line-height:15px;margin-top:2px;">
      <span style="color:#C0392B;font-weight:600;">Overdue · was due 1 Jul 2026</span>
      <span style="color:#4A5A70;"> · Required · official requirement</span>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;color:#5B6B80;margin-top:2px;word-break:break-all;">Official source: https://example.gob.es/tramite</div>
  </div><div style="page-break-inside:avoid;padding:8px 0 8px 12px;border-left:3px solid #2B5AA3;border-bottom:1px solid #D8D2C8;">
    <div style="font-size:12px;line-height:16px;color:#15243B;">Title of anchored-step</div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;line-height:15px;margin-top:2px;">
      <span style="color:#4A5A70;font-weight:600;">Starts once your residency is established</span>
      <span style="color:#4A5A70;"> · Required · official requirement</span>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;color:#5B6B80;margin-top:2px;word-break:break-all;">Official source: https://example.gob.es/tramite</div>
  </div><div style="page-break-inside:avoid;padding:8px 0 8px 12px;border-left:3px solid #5E7355;border-bottom:1px solid #D8D2C8;">
    <div style="font-size:12px;line-height:16px;color:#5E7355;text-decoration:line-through;text-decoration-thickness:1px;">✓ Title of done-step</div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;line-height:15px;margin-top:2px;">
      <span style="color:#5E7355;font-weight:600;">Done · 2 Jul 2026</span>
      <span style="color:#4A5A70;"> · Required · official requirement</span>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:10px;color:#5B6B80;margin-top:2px;word-break:break-all;">Official source: https://example.gob.es/tramite</div>
  </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:24px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid #D8D2C8;font-size:10px;line-height:15px;color:#5B6B80;">
    Estimated dates sharpen as real dates are confirmed; steps without dates begin once their milestone happens — Get Camino never invents a deadline.
